            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "銅價躍升 Freeport宣布Grasberg礦山供應遭遇不可抗力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> （本文為機器翻譯，準確性基於第三方軟件服務，反饋請點擊）</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">銅價周三躍升，此前Freeport McMoRan Inc.表示，其位於印度尼西亞的巨型礦山Grasberg的合同供應已遭遇不可抗力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">倫敦金屬交易所三個月期銅價格一度上漲2%，至每噸10,172美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司周三在一份聲明中表示，在9月8日Grasberg發生事故後，兩名工人不幸身亡。公司仍在搜尋另外五名工人。各支隊伍正晝夜不停清理泥漿與雜物，並在穩步推進，努力到達泥流事故發生時工人所在的區域。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3b7f8f97-0029-3675-b938-c9d34a4fa1a9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Freeport還給出了第三季度指引。與7月的預估相比，合併銷售預計銅將低約4%，黃金將低約6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Grasberg是全球第二大銅礦。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Copper Jumps After Freeport Declares Force Majeure at Grasberg</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8A%85%E5%83%B9%E8%BA%8D%E5%8D%87-freeport%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83grasberg%E7%A4%A6%E5%B1%B1%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E9%81%AD%E9%81%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%8A%97%E5%8A%9B-130213054.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-24 21:45:44",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國加大採購阿根廷大豆 因出口稅意外暫停",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國又買入至少10船阿根廷大豆，利用這個南美國家暫停出口稅之機在中美貿易戰之際加緊儲備。美國是中國的第二大供應國。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，進口商周二迅速買下這批貨，主要將於11月裝運。此前，布宜諾斯艾利斯暫停大豆等主要農產品出口關稅，觸發買盤熱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國農業部數據顯示，截至9月11日，新銷售季開始已有近兩周，中國尚未預訂任何一船美國大豆，為1999年有記錄以來首次，這表明北京再次在對美貿易戰中以農業為籌碼。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5083d14c-52fa-3b98-879a-b9776bd6e505-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">來自阿根廷的供應將緩解中國今年年底至2026年第一季度可能出現的供應缺口，在此期間，這個亞洲國家通常依賴占據市場主導地位的美國供應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">未獲授權公開發言的知情人士稱，本周預訂的阿根廷大豆總計至少在20船，超過130萬噸。知情人士稱，只要阿根廷意外減免出口關稅措施仍在實施，中國進口商預計將繼續從該國訂購大豆。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Buys More Argentine Soybeans as Tax Relief Spurs Trade</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E5%A4%A7%E8%B1%86-%E5%9B%A0%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E7%A8%85%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C-121307025.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-24 20:50:40",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "抖音電商GMV據報按年增34%　貨架電商增速表現特出",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"字節跳動旗下抖音電商GMV據報按年增34%，貨架電商增速表現特出。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"528\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/84IU7Y3yX0sf5oNHa2NUsw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2MztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/am730_578/ff625db63afa3ebc4a655856af2eab37\" width=\"900\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:900px\">字節跳動旗下抖音電商GMV據報按年增34%，貨架電商增速表現特出。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據內地傳媒報道，字節跳動旗下抖音在去年8月至今年7月期間，電商訂單總商品交易額(GMV)按年增長34%。其中，抖音貨架電商GMV上升49%，高於電商整體增速。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">抖音不予回應</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">而在今年「618活動」期間，抖音貨架電商GMV據報達2,000億人民幣(下同)。對於相關數字，抖音方面表示不予回應。去年抖音電商GMV約3.5萬億元，按年增長30%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">內地電商大戰近年愈演愈烈，其中外賣、即時零售等領域競爭最為激烈，惟報道引述一位接近抖音電商人士表示，抖音電商現階段不會過度捲入幾家大平台的即時零售戰爭。這意味著抖音電商將集中更多資源做電商業務，以提升電商的服務與體驗。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/抖音電商gmv據報按年增34-貨架電商增速表現特出/602632?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/抖音電商gmv據報按年增34-貨架電商增速表現特出/602632?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/抖音電商gmv據報按年增34-貨架電商增速表現特出/602632?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8A%96%E9%9F%B3%E9%9B%BB%E5%95%86gmv%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%8C%89%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%9E34-%E8%B2%A8%E6%9E%B6%E9%9B%BB%E5%95%86%E5%A2%9E%E9%80%9F%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E7%89%B9%E5%87%BA-114500496.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-24 20:35:39",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "惠譽將泰國評級展望下調至負面 因政治不確定且經濟前景弱化",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VxydUm19Tp4ppyPFckKwkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8eaea47d803ad4e1824537d1e76893a2\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 惠譽評級將泰國評級展望從穩定下調至負面，理由是長期政治不確定性與經濟成長前景疲軟正加劇公共財政風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">惠譽確認了泰國長期外幣發行人違約評級在「BBB+」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">惠譽在周三晚間發布的聲明中指出，由於多年實施大規模刺激措施，且財政整頓屢屢推遲，泰國的財政緩衝已遭侵蝕 —— 8月份政府一般性債務總額占國內生產毛額比例攀升至59.4%，逼近「BBB」評級的中位數水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Gg5Y2ciRs2iIs5b_v0NABw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3a6a1067bc7b08bc9767324ef3d5ee43\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fitch Cuts Thailand Outlook to Negative on Political Uncertainty</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cd49d0d5-dcb3-3a54-b2a2-3e22a8764a69-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Malavika Kaur Makol.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
